title: Savina Yannatou with Primavera en Salonico - Songs Of The Medite
description:
This recording is a Greek only release long before Manfred Eicher signed Savina and her band to ECM label. She's the best Greek female singer , her vocal technique is awsome and the timbre of her voice is just ethereal. No wonder why the ECM releases "Sumiglia" and "Songs Of An Other" received such fervent critics worldwide. Luckily the pressing contained an English booklet which I scanned.
 A TRUE SINGING GODDESS.

ENJOY!!!
